        "<div style='text-align: center;'>\n<h3>THE WOMAN OF EXETER</h3>\n<p>There dwelt an old woman at Exeter;</p>\n<p>When visitors came it sore vexed her,</p>\n<p>So for fear they should eat,</p>\n<p>She locked up all her meat,</p>\n<p>This stingy old woman of Exeter.</p>\n</div>",
